        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Suno证明了当Rapper是真没门槛｜AI 鲜测]]></title>
        <id>2247560014_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247560014&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b10013c7fa433d1b3126e7d5e233844a&amp;chksm=c236f18cf541789afd4d479e68788c038d9864ac66c3301f3a5dcd38061a3a83a75efe73e5ba#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-03-31T01:33:41.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p class="mp_vote_iframe_wrp" style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(122, 121, 121);line-height: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="236" data-backw="506" data-imgfileid="100016266" data-ratio="0.46574074074074073" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Sjq3CMC6G8ibXbzQx4XrgeKlECZeFbc7P2L0ZiaAw7qTGV011cibZLZyyyt1pNb2M0ED3lJ5TXWQGmw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 72px 0px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244 243 240);color: rgb(132 138 145);line-height: 24px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244 243 240);color: rgb(43 42 42);line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">对于普通人来说，写一首歌是一件难事：</span></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(43, 42, 42);line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">作词、作曲、编曲、录制这套流程下来，不仅要有乐理知识，也要对各个乐器的理解度，而且对于设备的要求也很高。</span></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(43, 42, 42);line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">之前民谣口碑不太好，稍微会点吉他能弹唱就会被称作歌手。后来 <strong>Rapper</strong> 拯救了民谣，成为了<strong>门槛最低的“音乐创作者”</strong>。</span></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(43, 42, 42);line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">不过门槛再低，至少我之前是做不出一首说唱歌曲，我不会做 Beat、不会混音，对于</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">音乐的一切我都是个门外汉。</span></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(43, 42, 42);line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">我这两天用 Suno 肝出来一千</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">多首歌，我真的能做出来让我自己单曲循环一段时间的Rap Music，我能写歌给自己听了。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(43, 42, 42);line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">我发现在 AI时代，第一个大规模失业的可能就是 Rapper。</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="visibility: visible;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(122, 121, 121);line-height: 24px;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="303" data-backw="506" data-height="1386" data-imgfileid="100016267" data-ratio="0.6" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2310" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Sjq3CMC6G8ibXbzQx4XrgeKl8bZm1fvKuo2tDDuFWmRySPWT8EqJ49j5mebJWddgXWnqEktKWeKjg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(122, 121, 121);line-height: 24px;text-a