        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="558" data-backw="558" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="574" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="197" data-imgfileid="100015848" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBI8D0qXQZ37QRiae4IxwWWPzq5eGmagvAS5IjfBmjUVZbkzrZPtLibSPVkrtTpWiaetPuMmdXvgBg40A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">最近，Kimi Chat 的上下文长度从 20 万汉字升级到了 200 万汉字，10 倍的差距已经足够产生一次质变，做很多之前做不了的事情。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">感谢月之暗面给了提前测试的机会，我们直接开测！</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">小伙伴可以上手试试啦！</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 16px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="will-change: transform;"><div style="margin: 48px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><div style="padding-left: 30px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin-bottom: -30px;transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="display: inline-block;width: 30px;height: 30px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 100%;border-style: none;border-color: rgba(118, 178, 124, 0);background-color: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);"><div powered-by="xiumi.us"><p><br></p></div></div></div><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="transform: translate3d(-15px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="padding-top: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);"><p><strong>场景1：做SEO（搜索引擎优化）！</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">第一轮测试用的是常规20万上下文窗口，</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">输入了两段网页代码，显然两轮对话已经超出20万上下文。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">这时候 200 万汉字的上下文长度的优势就显现出来了，直接转到200万字上下文入口重新提问，如果按照刚刚对话的 token 数量来算的话，目前至少能支持10轮及以上的对话。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="430" data-backw="578" data-height="1184" data-imgfileid="100015824" data-ratio="0.7435185185185185" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1592" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCYibV14AtMZgp6pmIQwhQQtYWMQBcWBf8wYMk5nkB45AQwsibrv0rrPog/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">20万上下文对话窗口：</span><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">分两次输入两段代码直接超出20w</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">第二轮测试：用200万窗口测试，这种持续连贯对话的感觉简直太爽了！</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">直接复制刚才的代码到200万窗口，它可一点儿没含糊，不停地持续回答和输出。然后直接问 Kimi 这个网站有啥可以改进的，它给了大概框架。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="580" data-backw="558" data-height="1818" data-imgfileid="100015825" data-ratio="1.0398148148148147" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1748" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCgBHUWicZicdcrAuLibfFhLfMfrwSSaE2MfbRQxvbyHWtqJm2iaMnIc100Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">200万上下文对话窗口：</span><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">超级无限长的代码10万字段儿，足足划了半分钟才到头儿</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">但我想要的是具体细致的建议，</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">接下来我又问它，具体有什么可以优化的地方；</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="920" data-backw="558" data-height="2863" data-imgfileid="100015826" data-ratio="1.6490740740740741" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1736" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCasOLU9LGqqaQdSlsHQUjm7MM7jO3N0IC1cRMCYsvguG2yvuDJlpB7g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">在这两次对话中，网站 SEO 优化建议是有了，但是我需要的是具体能够运行的代码，接下来测测它到底能否理解我的要求并给出相关的代码；</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">在回答具体建议时 Kimi 展开了每一条，优化的地方有十几处，Kimi 逐个给出了 SEO 优化建议及代码示例。（代码实在太长了就不一一展开了）</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">但是也有一个缺点：就是每次输出内容篇幅有限，又不能直接生成 PDF，就只能手动不停地点“继续、继续、继续......”</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="452" data-backw="558" data-height="1414" data-imgfileid="100015828" data-ratio="0.8092592592592592" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1748" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCibhibBrxKNTwicpia8uicqoOfdxkHBaY6lB38riaxHc2XbmMygSrknicy3ACQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">到这里之后，在元数据上进行优化，大方向上不会破坏原来的内容，Kimi 这点理解的还是挺到位的！在优化上甚至还多加了一些我没考虑到的点，十分周到。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="457" data-backw="558" data-height="1406" data-imgfileid="100015827" data-ratio="0.8194444444444444" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1716" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfC7gslmOezicMjGuXurNPQg937xYmgXTD5USE05uCr5as5BdicK9OpK9CQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">在前几次的回答中仍然不太满意，我想要的是最终在原数据上优化后的代码，于是再次要求它；</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="2362" data-backw="558" data-height="7502" data-imgfileid="100015831" data-ratio="4.233333333333333" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1772" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCqAD4RxzhZGhyUkUKjoqd35FMpiaF0jBrGAvHRiaVDn9hnf1lVNmLlxjQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">从理解能力和连贯性来看，Kimi 每次回答都能相对准确地联系上下文，同时给出相应的建议，可见它在长文本连贯性上是蛮强的！</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">现在我们来实际看一下，优化SEO网站之后的实际效果到底如何？</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">这次对话对网站的 SEO 优化最直观体现在这三个地方：</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">第一，图片和视频在网页中的占比有所调整。</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">比如第一个视频整体变小，第二张图也变的稍微小一些；</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">（PS：左为原网站，右为优化 SEO 后的网站）</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="266" data-backw="558" data-height="1378" data-imgfileid="100015833" data-ratio="0.4759259259259259" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2896" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCbpnbWap2cgSJ7cU9IWzQjMVLXbv5kUibupibQItVj1UHpR3gMOKHwgcA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="275" data-backw="578" data-height="1392" data-imgfileid="100015840" data-ratio="0.4759259259259259" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="2926" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCTOj3phoNyk8owsIoTYRqh5JpRXRB7iaya6cstdXoeyAzMzhuqO2MMLg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">第二，页面整体布局更加协调，更加符合视觉习惯</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">，对比着看确实舒服不少。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="278" data-backw="578" data-height="1386" data-imgfileid="100015832" data-ratio="0.48148148148148145" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2880" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCGOhppsO3wJm9yjvMrOU3dXQzRIPQ4PVia0c3Syu0GYPawqZNmXIOl9g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">第三，网页文字内容优化</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">，在原来的基础上优化了网页里呈现的文字内容，</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="279" data-backw="578" data-height="1398" data-imgfileid="100015829" data-ratio="0.48333333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2894" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfC29bEicz9rm4kqex5k9NOLLvGs9baJSjQ0rs2YwnCRXhSrnnrOHQXhWg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 16px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="will-change: transform;"><div style="margin: 48px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><div style="padding-left: 30px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin-bottom: -30px;transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="display: inline-block;width: 30px;height: 30px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 100%;border-style: none;border-color: rgba(118, 178, 124, 0);background-color: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);"><div powered-by="xiumi.us"><p><br></p></div></div></div><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="transform: translate3d(-15px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="padding-top: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);"><p><strong>场景2：我用《周易》给奥特曼算了一卦！</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">大型语言模型处理古文字与处理现代英文的差异时，一个显著的区别在于所需的编码单元或"token"的数量。古文字，如《周易》中的八卦符号，每个符号可能需要一个或多个 tokens 来准确表示其丰富的意义和历史背景，因为这些符号往往蕴含着比现代字母更复杂的概念。相比之下，现代英文文字则相对简单，通常每个字符对应一个token，因为它们的语义和形式更直接、更线性。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="328" data-backw="558" data-height="705" data-imgfileid="100015834" data-ratio="0.5879629629629629" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCsKn5aSia6IqxtdkWC2Aw8OxFZjIvuLCHIGGMW43xwEbUCZmv6heV5cw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">图片源自网络</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">基于此，我就借用咱们的经典《周易》给奥特曼先生算一卦，看看 Kimi 在解读《周易》古文字上的效果如何。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">我先是上传了中华经典《周易》典藏本，和奥特曼的生辰八字（约莫准确？）</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="421" data-backw="558" data-imgfileid="100015841" data-ratio="0.7537037037037037" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCv6Iah6vNOBG5HSZIR633dNhbNFQQyCg2nYpt0ibIRvricicO41dNeAXtQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">图片由 Midjourney 生成</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">从第一次回答中，能看出 Kimi 在解读古文字时说的头头是道，像模像样。让我们继续深入看看它到底专业不？</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="702" data-backw="578" data-height="2114" data-imgfileid="100015835" data-ratio="1.2148148148148148" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1740" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCtdfy3YqPLiavzZZicRVXLGicEAg4txEkAvrLRHjyXVp9hC7eXdIxIGicug/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">接下来我又给出奥特曼的一些生平履历，</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">Kimi 一开始的回答很浅很浅，都没啥意思；</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">但提醒它深入分析后，还是很浅！！</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">看来《周易》这种难啃的古文字对 Kimi 来说还是挺有难度的。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="1073" data-backw="578" data-height="3240" data-imgfileid="100015837" data-ratio="1.8574074074074074" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1744" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCZ9IVEbfKribldxWZtac44c5G8wPlsINuvSibRLjXpgbcruBh4AnNsQHA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 16px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="will-change: transform;"><div style="margin: 48px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><div style="padding-left: 30px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin-bottom: -30px;transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="display: inline-block;width: 30px;height: 30px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 100%;border-style: none;border-color: rgba(118, 178, 124, 0);background-color: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);"><div powered-by="xiumi.us"><p><br></p></div></div></div><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="transform: translate3d(-15px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="padding-top: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);"><p><strong>场景3：我用 Kimi 啃专业论文！</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">原本是想根据个人一年的工作材料，让 Kimi 写一个年终报告，但是现在三月份，还没到那时候呢！</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">那如果是论文呢？</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">如果它连大几十的论文都啃得动，能理解并且连续输出重新写一篇新的论文，个人年终总结更是不在话下！</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">下面我上传了31份 AI 相关的热门论文，kimi 能从大量晦涩难懂的论文中，迅速分析并输出新的论文大纲，大纲内容角度还挺全面。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="647" data-backw="558" data-height="1998" data-imgfileid="100015836" data-ratio="1.1592592592592592" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1724" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCo5yW9qKoPz1oAzQ8GgzTnk8kibeN7a4ltCnIyQWhx3HMBQqRLlRWkYg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">这部分不仅提炼出了新的主题，同时用中英文对照的方式写了出来，还列出表格对比了新旧论文的主要观点。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">最初想法是写一篇论文，那自然要看看他能提出哪些独到的观点，看他是否真的理解了这些论文的内容，然后从这些观点中选择一个主题写出论文大纲；</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="866" data-backw="558" data-imgfileid="100015842" data-ratio="1.5518518518518518" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCdVlf4Be4Adz0CSz17MucRVlnmwHZsk5JtEBPeTbTOoJjeTn0LQVXgA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">接下来就是撰写正文了，对于 Kimi 输出内容质量倒是没那么担心，不过 Kimi 有个缺点是每一次的输出篇幅偏短，想要让它一次写长论文，基本没可能。倒是 Kimi 自己在结尾也提醒到了“篇幅有限”这一点。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">如果想要<strong>更精细</strong>的内容，更好的办法是<span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>把论文大纲拆分成小章节单独扩写</strong></span>，才能达到想要的效果。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="253" data-backw="558" data-height="790" data-imgfileid="100015839" data-ratio="0.4527777777777778" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1746" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCXmhzh0Qichqlt9OAkeibm9AZOs0uyYAQxKhY07gMUfhayLKyibiaMkmV2Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-align: justify;margin: 8px 8px 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="326" data-backw="578" data-height="922" data-imgfileid="100015838" data-ratio="0.5638888888888889" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1634" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7QrGgzqg5ZVQ0BuK9yWeMfCUTHsCc7MhLUWcslYsFIzicIzTkia9xD3ecUmErAia0maUGRtyutC5dgaA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">这个测试极大地体现出来 Kimi 对于上下文的高度连续性，对于工作中处理大量的文献以及资料 十分方便，尤其是想要提取特定的信息的时候。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">通过这次测试，最大的感受是：上下文带来不仅仅 AI 的学习能力，<strong>更重要的是<span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);">让 AI 的耐力更强，我们可以持续进行多轮对话。</span></strong></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">超长文本输入+持续的多轮对话能力，我们在一个对话中就能将 AI 微调成我们需要的样子。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">月之暗面创始人 杨植麟认为：“所有问题都是文本长度的问题。如果你有10亿的 context length（上下文长度），今天看到的问题都不是问题。”</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">对于长文本来说更重要的是 lossless，也就是输入的信息不随着文本长度增加而损失。某种程度上，绝对的文本长度是花架子，无损压缩的能力才能分模型的胜负。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">月之暗面方面透露，这次上下文长度从20万字扩展到200万字由于没有采用常规的渐进式提升路线，研发和技术团队遇到的技术难度也是指数级增加的。为了达到更好的⻓窗口无损压缩性能，团队从模型预训练到对⻬、推理环节均进行了原生的重新设计和开发。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">期待月之暗面 10 亿上下文的那一天，也欢迎各位读者将自己使用 Kimi Chat的经验和心得分享给我们， 探索200 万汉字的潜力到底在哪里。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="187" data-backw="562" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100071130" data-ratio="0.3333333333333333" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJ0DYCno5RzN8105rkhDwDHq1mZMrRPt0EAKiadoIqmicia2RvxgABjSIpOrGy3b8ltYce6fQ8r4e1ew/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="32" data-backw="578" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100075719" data-ratio="0.05555555555555555" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;width: 562px;visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJaK5QKXpZfwqNOe7NgDCtIKwOv9cIESEKkfoTJwSQmDGHKhaeuMAyndwawXPiaZrVbfToW2F6h4ng/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=wxpic"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);text-align: right;"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247559474&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7004e06a09695e6245773017b9414220&amp;chksm=c236f3f0f5417ae62fb62f1c5a4c058660822877874e0b901db44b50798c8aab1efb48945a58&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100075721" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ90huia1giaPNH2yiaofibDrnRiaibOfwfGnKaMKKmIE9VeIgDCpvcn2lOcoZoqIe7ltTibyyfrPqoYLaTQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247559187&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b6b35f34d695afe44caeb05affc68f1c&amp;chksm=c236f2d1f5417bc77626b608a277474c5fc8b5ffc1e678cd314c9add37c95dc1964287ed122a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100075720" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBI8D0qXQZ37QRiae4IxwWWPzBoYoMplnWJzT6LEw3aia7ibcru6pc6nicMk8cfs5JY84aibYPNiakgOzKlA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247559187&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=c68f36211380dfc2c8652e3d7ac3109a&amp;chksm=c236f2d1f5417bc72525afeb0c2c7b30b787760bc79b963e8eb7cf1d766e467577082d546e1f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100075722" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initi